data.name: Needle Wall
data.desc: Once per turn, during your Standby Phase: Roll a six-sided die. Treat your opponent's Main Monster Zones as numbers 1-5, counting from your right, and destroy the monster that is in the same Main Monster Zone as the result. If the result is 6, roll again.

card_sets.set_name: Legendary Collection 4: Joey's World Mega Pack
